Notes

  • We definitely need to check why July is an object, when it is meant to be a float.
  • Could consider turning the seperate columns of months into two columns one to say the month and one for the price

    • Visualization ideas

  • Average per month
  • Average per fuel type(by month and by year)
  • Comparison of Coastal and In land prices (by year and by fuel type)
  • Is there a way to forecast future fuel prices?
  • Detecting anomolies - was there ever a month that the price just seemed way too out there in comparison to the rest of the prices for that fuel type
  • Basic stuff - like maximum and minimum price per month, also by year and by type
